html
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    title zeevi music
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/css/foundation.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/css/signup.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/css/style.css')
    script(src='/js/vendor/modernizr.js')
  body
    include header
    br
    br
    .row
      .small-6.large-centered.columns.bound
        h1
          | Regístrate en Zeevi
      .small-6.large-centered.columns.bound
        form(method="post",action="/api/user/new")
          .row
            .large-12.columns
              input(type='text', name='username', placeholder='Nombre de usuario')
          .row
            .large-12.columns
              input(type='password', name='password' placeholder='Contraseña')
          .row
            .large-12.columns
              input(type='text', name='email' placeholder='e-mail')
          .row
            .large-12.columns
              label Tipo de registro:
              input#band(type='radio', name='tipo', value='1')
              label(for='band') Banda
              input#venue(type='radio', name='tipo', value='2')
              label(for='venue') Venue
              input#fan(type='radio', name='tipo', value='3')
              label(for='fan') Fan
          .row
            .large-12.columns

              input(type="submit", class="expand button",value="Enviar")
              p.small-word
                | Al presionar el botón de "Enviar", usted acepta todos los terminos y condiciones.
        .row
          .large-12.columns
            p
              | ¿Ya eres miebro de Zeevi?
              a(href='../login') Entrar.
    .footer
      // footer
